text: Gaetano De Vescovi (born 14 November 1937) is an Italian wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Italy Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Trieste
